{"tid":200893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一眼 vs 慢慢了解","createTime":"2017-04-14T10:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T04:23:29.000Z","uid":13738,"like":41,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7ab0821c0faf3b4851409ff749e4906f13d24b","tid":200893,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:49:50.000Z","msg":"成日都聽到有兩種說法<br />\n有人話第一眼見一個人 , 聽佢講第一句說話已經知佢係咩野人，判定左佢係點，應該做普通朋友、好朋友、情人<br />\n都有人話<br />\n應該慢慢了解，做住普通朋友，慢慢了解，有機會先繼續發展<br />\n但各有利弊<br />\n第一眼就判斷人既，可能根本唔了解對方，任憑你睇得幾透都好，都好易走漏眼<br />\n慢慢黎既，好似又會好易因為了解而分開，或者好易fdzone人<br />\n唔知巴絲點睇？<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 第一眼<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :  慢慢認識再發展"},{"pid":"7473ddcf42dad3fcd5bf9b7e01abc01b5111c87d","tid":200893,"uid":10925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"基本上咁分。 <br />\n靚仔= 正皮， <br />\n油頭毒=負皮"},{"pid":"3348134471ac585e2406729a1de07412e1a64dea","tid":200893,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上咁分。 <br />\n靚仔= 正皮， <br />\n油頭毒=負皮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問得緊係排除左樣既問題<br />\n港女應該唔係個個咁膚淺掛"},{"pid":"74a05648604de3258266031f7d55fabcd677f354","tid":200893,"uid":22693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"第一眼有興趣之後再慢慢了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd44cfc641df4d6667cd350bbb7a14568b4707a","tid":200893,"uid":103728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"我係男，第一眼見面，就感覺到岩唔岩feel ,<br />\n<br />\n如果對佢有feel, 之後先會想慢慢了解。<br />\n<br />\n如果無feel就直接係普通朋友，<im